e suppression and control of ^beam A_LR's. We also\npresent results on beam performance from engineering and physics runs for\nE-158.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Sep 2002 20:08:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2002 19:19:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
